room_title: Escape room "Operation Counterpart" by Eludesions Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_address: 2710 W Bell Road, Suite 1200, Phoenix, AZ 85053
room_description:
Sam is a fellow CIA agent assigned to your task force which is charged with protecting a special weapon here in Phoenix.  After Sam twice fails to check-in, standard protocol dictates a team is assembled to locate the agent’s whereabouts. 
You and your team begin by visiting Sam’s place of residence. When you arrive at Sam’s apartment you find the door ajar and room ransacked.  After initially clearing the apartment for any hostiles, you realize something is very wrong and you begin to investigate.
